# Streamlit Auth Pattern

- Always get the Supabase client via `get_authenticated_client()` from `src/datapulse/streamlit_auth.py`.
- Do not create new unauthenticated clients in `pages/*.py` (avoid direct `create_client(...)`).
- Use `st.session_state["user"]["id"]` (or helper functions that read it) for `user_id` in page queries.

